title: THE BILL DANA SHOW -- The Honeymoon Suite ( First Season )
description:
Jewish comedian Bill Dana played bumbling Latino Jose Jimenez in at least four TV series ( including two versions of The Steve Allen Show ) before he again portrayed Jose in several Seasons 9 & 10 episodes of The Danny Thomas Show.  Danny decided to give Bill his own series during the final season of his own sitcom, and this was the result.

Guest Stars -- Simon Oakland, Barbara Stuart, and semi-regular Don Adams
